     ******************************************************************
     **  プログラム名   : 試作番地マスタ保守　　　　　　　　     **
     **  プログラムＩＤ :  MRHR11     <RPG>                        **
     **  作成年月日     :  2014/01/17                              **
     **  作成者         :  TR-ITS                                  **
     **  プログラム概要 : 試作番地マスタのメンテナンスをおこなう **
     **--------------------------------------------------------------**
     **  変更年月日     :  YYYY/MM/DD                              **
     **  変更者         :                                          **
     **  変更内容       :                                          **
     ******************************************************************
     ** <<使用標識説明>>
     **        01       :プログラム終了 <F01>
     **        03       :前画面に戻る   <F03>
     **        05       :更新処理       <F05>
     **        06       :スクラップ更新 <F06>
     **     41～58    :画面共通エラー標識（全画面共通）
     **        80       :試作番地マスタ読込
     **     81～82    :他ファイル読込
     **        88       : LOOKUP(*EQ)
     **        90       :更新区分＝０（削除）＋　画面プロテクト
     **        91       :更新区分＝１（変更）
     **        92       :更新区分＝２（追加）
     **        99       :代表エラー標識
     ******************************************************************
     H            Y/                                    1
     **==============================================================**
     **  ファイル
     **==============================================================**
     F*<<試作番地マスタ保守　画面>>
     FMRHPW11 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     F                                              KINFDS WSDS
     F*<<試作番地マスタ>>
     FMRHPL11 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     F*<<部品情報マスタ>>
     FMRHPL21 IF  E           K        DISK
     **==============================================================**
     **  配列
     **==============================================================**
     E                    @SL     1   3  6                SELECT
     E                    @MS     1   8 53                ERR MSG
     **==============================================================**
     **  ＤＳ
     **==============================================================**
     I*<<システム情報>>
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM S@PGID
     I                                      244 253 S@WSID
     I                                      254 263 S@USID
     I                                      264 269 S@JBID
     I*<<システム日時>>
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140S@TIME
     I                                        1   60S@HMS
     I                                        1   20S@TMHH
     I                                        3   40S@TMMM
     I                                        5   60S@TMSS
     I                                        7  140S@YYMD
     I                                        7  100S@DYYY
     I                                       11  120S@DYMM
     I                                       13  140S@DYDD
     I*<<カーソル制御>>
     IWSDS        DS
     I                                    B 370 3710S@CUR
     I                                      370 370 S@LIN
     I                                      371 371 S@COL
     I                                    B 378 3790S@POS
     **--------------------------------------------------------------**
     I* <<共通>>
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80W@SYMD
     I                                        1   20W@SMM
     I                                        3   40W@SDD
     I                                        5   80W@SYY4
     I            DS
     I                                        1   8 W@SEL
     I                                        1   1 W@SEL1
     I                                        2   2 W@HF
     I                                        3   8 W@SEL2
     **==============================================================**
     **  パラメータ
     **==============================================================**
      *
     **==============================================================**
     **  ＫＥＹ
     **==============================================================**
     C* <<試作番地マスタ(MRHPL11) >>
     C           SBKEY     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           SBBAN1           *番地１
     C                     KFLD           SBBAN2           *番地２
     C                     KFLD           SBBAN3           *番地３
     C                     KFLD           SBBAN4           *番地４
     C* <<部品情報マスタ(MRHPL21) >>
     C           EAKEY     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           EASHN1           *社内品番１
     C                     KFLD           EASHN2           *社内品番２
     C                     KFLD           EASHN3           *社内品番３
     C                     KFLD           EASEHI           *製品区分
     C                     KFLD           EATEHI           *手配区分
     **==============================================================**
     **  メインルーチン
     **==============================================================**
      *
      *---<初期処理>---*
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      *
      *---<主処理>---*
     C           W@NEXT    DOUEQ'END  '                    ¬DO_01
      * G1
     C           W@NEXT    CASEQ'SET10'   #SET10           ~¬CAS
     C           W@NEXT    CASEQ'PNL10'   #PNL10            |
     C           W@NEXT    CASEQ'CHK10'   #CHK10            |
      * G2
     C           W@NEXT    CASEQ'SET20'   #SET20            |
     C           W@NEXT    CASEQ'PNL20'   #PNL20            |
     C           W@NEXT    CASEQ'CHK20'   #CHK20            |
     C           W@NEXT    CASEQ'WIN20'   #WIN20            |
      *
     C           W@NEXT    CASEQ'DBOUT'   #DBOUT            |
     C                     END                             _｢CAS
      *
     C                     END                             ｢DO_01
      *
      *---<終了処理>---*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
      **************************************************************************
      *         Ｓ　Ｕ　Ｂ　－　Ｒ　Ｏ　Ｕ　Ｔ　Ｉ　Ｎ　Ｅ
      **************************************************************************
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #INIT    初期処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C                     TIME           S@TIME
     C                     Z-ADDS@DYMM    W@SMM
     C                     Z-ADDS@DYDD    W@SDD
     C                     Z-ADDS@DYYY    W@SYY4
     C                     Z-ADDW@SYMD    D1SYMD           * SYSTEM DATE
      *
     C                     MOVEL'S'       W@SEHI  1        *製品区分
     C                     MOVEL'S'       W@TEHI  1        *手配区分
      *
      * NEXT-CONTROL
     C                     MOVEL'SET10'   W@NEXT  5
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #SET10   第一画面(G1) 項目セット処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #SET10    BEGSR
      *
     C                     SETOF                     909192
     C                     SETOF                     414243
     C                     SETOF                     4445
     C                     SETOF                     99
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D1SELC           *更新区分
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D1BAN1           *番地１
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D1BAN2           *番地２
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D1BAN3           *番地３
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D1BAN4           *番地４
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D1EMSG           * ERR MSG
      *
      * NEXT-CONTROL
     C                     MOVEL'PNL10'   W@NEXT           G1-PNL
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #PNL10   第一画面(G1) 表示処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #PNL10    BEGSR
      *
     C                     EXFMTMRHPW111
      *
     C                     SETOF                     909192
     C                     SETOF                     414243
     C                     SETOF                     4445
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D1EMSG           * ERR MSG
      *
      * NEXT-CONTROL
     C                     MOVEL'CHK10'   W@NEXT
      * CF03
     C           *IN01     IFEQ '1'                        ¬IF_01
     C                     MOVEL'END  '   W@NEXT
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *
     C           *IN12     IFEQ '1'                        ¬IF_01
     C                     CALL 'MRHR12'
     C                     PARM           D1BAN1  1
     C                     PARM           D1BAN2  2
     C                     PARM           D1BAN3  2
     C                     PARM           D1BAN4  1
     C                     MOVEL'PNL10'   W@NEXT
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #CHK10   第一画面(G1) チェック処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #CHK10    BEGSR
      *更新区分
     C           D1SELC    IFNE '0'                        ¬IF_01
     C           D1SELC    ANDNE'1'
     C           D1SELC    ANDNE'2'
     C  N99                MOVEL@MS,01    D1EMSG    P      * ERR MSG
     C  N99                SETON                     4199
      *
     C                     ELSE                            +ELSE_01
     C                     SELEC                           ~¬SELEC_01
     C           D1SELC    WHEQ '0'                        -+WHEN_01
     C                     SETON                     90    * DELETE
     C           D1SELC    WHEQ '1'                        -+WHEN_01
     C                     SETON                     91    * CHANGE
     C           D1SELC    WHEQ '2'                        -+WHEN_01
     C                     SETON                     92    * ADD
     C                     END                             _｢SELEC_01
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *番地
     C           D1BAN1    IFEQ *BLANK                     ¬IF_01
     C           D1BAN2    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C           D1BAN3    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C           D1BAN4    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C  N99                MOVEL@MS,02    D1EMSG    P      * ERR MSG
     C  N99                SETON                     424344
     C  N99                SETON                     4599
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *エラーなし
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '0'                        ¬IF_01
      *試作番地マスタ(MRHPL11)
     C                     MOVELD1BAN1    SBBAN1           *番地１
     C                     MOVELD1BAN2    SBBAN2           *番地２
     C                     MOVELD1BAN3    SBBAN3           *番地３
     C                     MOVELD1BAN4    SBBAN4           *番地４
     C           SBKEY     CHAINMRHPL111            N80
     C           *IN80     IFEQ '0'                        ~¬IF_02
      * ADD
     C           D1SELC    IFEQ '2'                        ~~¬IF_03
     C           SBGSJY    IFEQ 'D'                        ~~~¬IF_04
     C           SBGSHZ    ANDLES@YYMD
     C                     ELSE                            ---+ELSE_04
     C  N99                MOVEL@MS,05    D1EMSG    P      * ERR MSG
     C  N99                SETON                     424344
     C  N99                SETON                     4599
     C                     END                             ___｢IF_04
     C                     END                             __｢IF_03
      * CHANGE/DELETE
     C           D1SELC    IFEQ '0'                        ~~¬IF_03
     C           D1SELC    OREQ '1'
     C           SBGSJY    IFEQ 'D'                        ~~~¬IF_04
     C           SBGSHZ    ANDLES@YYMD
     C  N99                MOVEL@MS,04    D1EMSG    P      * ERR MSG
     C  N99                SETON                     424344
     C  N99                SETON                     4599
     C                     END                             ___｢IF_04
     C                     END                             __｢IF_03
      *
     C                     ELSE                            -+ELSE_02
      * CHANGE/DELETE
     C           D1SELC    IFEQ '0'                        ~~¬IF_03
     C           D1SELC    OREQ '1'
     C  N99                MOVEL@MS,03    D1EMSG    P      * ERR MSG
     C  N99                SETON                     424344
     C  N99                SETON                     4599
     C                     END                             __｢IF_03
      *
     C                     END                             _｢IF_02
      *
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *
      * NEXT-CONTROL
     C                     MOVEL'SET20'   W@NEXT
      *エラーあり
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '1'                        ¬IF_01
     C                     MOVEL'PNL10'   W@NEXT
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #SET20   第二画面(G2) 項目セット処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #SET20    BEGSR
      *
     C                     SETOF                     464748
     C                     SETOF                     495051
     C                     SETOF                     99
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2SEL            *更新区分／名称
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     D2HAKO           *番地サイズ
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2HIN1           *品番１
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2HIN2           *品番２
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2HIN3           *品番３
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2LNO1           *手配番号１
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2LNO2           *手配番号２
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2EMSG           * ERR MSG
      *
     C                     MOVELD1SELC    W@SEL1
     C                     MOVEL'-'       W@HF
     C                     SELEC                           ¬SELEC_01
     C           D1SELC    WHEQ '0'                        +WHEN_01
     C                     MOVEL@SL,01    W@SEL2
     C           D1SELC    WHEQ '1'                        +WHEN_01
     C                     MOVEL@SL,02    W@SEL2
     C           D1SELC    WHEQ '2'                        +WHEN_01
     C                     MOVEL@SL,03    W@SEL2
     C                     END                             ｢SELEC_01
     C                     MOVELW@SEL     D2SEL            *更新区分／名称
      * CHANGE/DELETE
     C           D1SELC    IFEQ '0'                        ¬IF_01
     C           D1SELC    OREQ '1'
     C                     Z-ADDSBHAKO    D2HAKO           *番地サイズ
     C                     MOVELSBHIN1    D2HIN1           *品番１
     C                     MOVELSBHIN2    D2HIN2           *品番２
     C                     MOVELSBHIN3    D2HIN3           *品番３
     C                     MOVELSBLNO1    D2LNO1           *手配番号１
     C                     MOVELSBLNO2    D2LNO2           *手配番号２
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *
      * NEXT-CONTROL
     C                     MOVEL'PNL20'   W@NEXT
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #PNL20   第二画面(G2) 表示処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #PNL20    BEGSR
      *
     C                     EXFMTMRHPW112
      *
     C                     SETOF                     464748
     C                     SETOF                     495051
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2EMSG           * ERR MSG
      *
      * NEXT-CONTROL
     C                     MOVEL'CHK20'   W@NEXT
      * CF03
     C           *IN03     IFEQ '1'                        ¬IF_01
     C                     MOVEL'PNL10'   W@NEXT
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #CHK20   第二画面(G2) チェック処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #CHK20    BEGSR
      * ADD/CHANGE
     C           D1SELC    IFEQ '1'                        ¬IF_01
     C           D1SELC    OREQ '2'
      *番地サイズ
     C           D2HAKO    IFEQ *ZERO                      ~¬IF_02
     C  N99                MOVEL@MS,06    D2EMSG    P      * ERR MSG
     C  N99                SETON                     4699
     C                     END                             _｢IF_02
      *品番
     C           D2HIN1    IFEQ *BLANK                     ~¬IF_02
     C           D2HIN2    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C           D2HIN3    ANDEQ*BLANK
      *
     C                     ELSE                            -+ELSE_02
      *部品情報マスタ(MRHPL21)
     C                     MOVELD2HIN1    EASHN1           *社内品番１
     C                     MOVELD2HIN2    EASHN2           *社内品番２
     C                     MOVELD2HIN3    EASHN3           *社内品番３
     C                     MOVELW@SEHI    EASEHI           *製品区分
     C                     MOVELW@TEHI    EATEHI           *手配区分
     C           EAKEY     CHAINMRHPL211             81
     C           *IN81     IFEQ '1'                        ~~¬IF_03
     C  N99                MOVEL@MS,07    D2EMSG    P      * ERR MSG
     C  N99                SETON                     474849
     C  N99                SETON                     99
      *
     C                     ELSE                            --+ELSE_03
     C           EAGSJY    IFEQ 'D'                        ~~~¬IF_04
     C           EAGSHZ    ANDLES@YYMD
     C  N99                MOVEL@MS,08    D2EMSG    P      * ERR MSG
     C  N99                SETON                     474849
     C  N99                SETON                     99
     C                     END                             ___｢IF_04
     C                     END                             __｢IF_03
      *
     C                     END                             _｢IF_02
      *
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W@SCFL  1        * SCRAPフラグ
      *
      * NEXT-CONTROL
     C                     MOVEL'PNL20'   W@NEXT
      * CF05
     C           *IN05     IFEQ '1'                        ¬IF_01
     C           *IN99     ANDEQ'0'
     C                     MOVEL'DBOUT'   W@NEXT
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      * CF06 & CHANGE
     C           *IN06     IFEQ '1'                        ¬IF_01
     C           D1SELC    ANDEQ'1'
     C           *IN99     ANDEQ'0'
     C                     EXSR #CLR20                     * CLEAR
     C                     MOVEL'WIN20'   W@NEXT
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #CLR20   クリア処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #CLR20    BEGSR
      *
     C                     SETOF                     99
      *
     C                     MOVELD2HIN1    W@HIN1  5        *品番１
     C                     MOVELD2HIN2    W@HIN2  5        *品番２
     C                     MOVELD2HIN3    W@HIN3  2        *品番３
     C                     MOVELD2LNO1    W@LNO1  4        *手配番号１
     C                     MOVELD2LNO2    W@LNO2  3        *手配番号２
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2HIN1           *品番１
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2HIN2           *品番２
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2HIN3           *品番３
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2LNO1           *手配番号１
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2LNO2           *手配番号２
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    D2EMSG           * ERR MSG
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W@SCFL           * SCRAPフラグ
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #WIN20   ＷＩＮＤＯＷ画面 (WINDOW) 表示処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #WIN20    BEGSR
      *
     C                     WRITEMRHPW112
     C                     EXFMTMRHPW113
      *
      * NEXT-CONTROL
     C                     MOVEL'WIN20'   W@NEXT
      * CF03
     C           *IN03     IFEQ '1'                        ¬IF_01
     C                     MOVELW@HIN1    D2HIN1           *品番１
     C                     MOVELW@HIN2    D2HIN2           *品番２
     C                     MOVELW@HIN3    D2HIN3           *品番３
     C                     MOVELW@LNO1    D2LNO1           *手配番号１
     C                     MOVELW@LNO2    D2LNO2           *手配番号２
     C                     MOVEL'PNL20'   W@NEXT
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      * CF05
     C           *IN05     IFEQ '1'                        ¬IF_01
     C                     MOVEL'DBOUT'   W@NEXT
     C                     MOVEL'1'       W@SCFL           * SCRAPフラグ
      *
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #DBOUT   Ｄ．Ｂ　アクセス処理
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #DBOUT    BEGSR
      *
     C                     TIME           S@TIME
      *
      *試作番地マスタ(MRHPL11)
     C                     MOVELD1BAN1    SBBAN1           *番地１
     C                     MOVELD1BAN2    SBBAN2           *番地２
     C                     MOVELD1BAN3    SBBAN3           *番地３
     C                     MOVELD1BAN4    SBBAN4           *番地４
     C           SBKEY     CHAINMRHPL111             80
      *
      * DELETE
     C           D1SELC    IFEQ '0'                        ¬IF_01
     C           *IN80     IFEQ '0'                        ~¬IF_02
     C                     EXSR #DEL10                     * DELETE(UPDAT)
     C                     END                             _｢IF_02
     C                     ELSE                            +ELSE_01
      * ADD / CHANGE
     C           *IN80     IFEQ '0'                        ~¬IF_02
      * ADD(UPDAT)
     C           D1SELC    IFEQ '2'                        ~~¬IF_03
     C                     EXSR #WRT11                     * WRITE(UPDAT)
     C                     END                             __｢IF_03
      * CHANGE
     C           D1SELC    IFEQ '1'                        ~~¬IF_03
     C                     EXSR #UPD10                     * UPDAT
     C                     END                             __｢IF_03
     C                     ELSE                            -+ELSE_02
      * ADD(WRITE)
     C                     EXSR #WRT10                     * WRITE
     C                     END                             _｢IF_02
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
      *
      * NEXT-CONTROL
     C                     MOVEL'SET10'   W@NEXT
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #WRT10   試作番地マスタ(MRHPL11)追加処理(WRITE)
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #WRT10    BEGSR
      *
     C                     CLEARMRHPL111
      *
     C                     Z-ADDS@YYMD    SBGKHZ           * UPDATE DATE
     C                     Z-ADDS@HMS     SBGKTM           * UPDATE TIME
     C                     MOVELS@PGID    SBGKPG           * UPDATE PROGRAM
     C                     MOVELS@USID    SBGKNM           * UPDATE PERSON
     C                     MOVELD1BAN1    SBBAN1           * LOCATION CODE 1
     C                     MOVELD1BAN2    SBBAN2           * LOCATION CODE 2
     C                     MOVELD1BAN3    SBBAN3           * LOCATION CODE 3
     C                     MOVELD1BAN4    SBBAN4           * LOCATION CODE 4
     C                     Z-ADDD2HAKO    SBHAKO           * LOCATION SIZE
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     SBSCHZ           * SCRAP DATE
     C                     Z-ADDS@YYMD    SBGRHZ           * ADD DATE
     C                     Z-ADDS@HMS     SBGRTM           * ADD TIME
     C                     MOVELS@PGID    SBGRPG           * ADD PROGRAM
     C                     MOVELS@USID    SBGRNM           * ADD PERSON'
      *
     C                     WRITEMRHPL111
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #WRT11   試作番地マスタ(MRHPL11)追加更新処理(UPDAT)
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #WRT11    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SBGSJY           * DELETE CODE D
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     SBGSHZ           * DELETE DATE
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SBGSNM           * DELETE PERSON
     C                     Z-ADDS@YYMD    SBGKHZ           * UPDATE DATE
     C                     Z-ADDS@HMS     SBGKTM           * UPDATE TIME
     C                     MOVELS@PGID    SBGKPG           * UPDATE PROGRAM
     C                     MOVELS@USID    SBGKNM           * UPDATE PERSON
     C                     Z-ADDD2HAKO    SBHAKO           * LOCATION SIZE
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SBHIN1           * PART NUMBER 1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SBHIN2           * PART NUMBER 2
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SBHIN3           * PART NUMBER 3
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SBLNO1           * LOT NO 1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SBLNO2           * LOT NO 2
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     SBSCHZ           * SCRAP DATE
      *
     C                     UPDATMRHPL111
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      *          #UPD10   試作番地マスタ(MRHPL11)更新処理(UPDAT)
      *-------------------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #UPD10    BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SBGSJY           * DELETE CODE D
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     SBGSHZ           * DELETE DATE
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    SBGSNM           * DELETE PERSON
     C                     Z-ADDS@YYMD    SBGKHZ           * UPDATE DATE
     C                     Z-ADDS@HMS     SBGKTM           * UPDATE TIME
     C                     MOVELS@PGID    SBGKPG           * UPDATE PROGRAM
     C                     MOVELS@USID    SBGKNM           * UPDATE PERSON
     C                     Z-ADDD2HAKO    SBHAKO           * LOCATION SIZE
     C                     MOVELD2HIN1    SBHIN1           * PART NUMBER 1
     C                     MOVELD2HIN2    SBHIN2           * PART NUMBER 2
     C                     MOVELD2HIN3    SBHIN3           * PART NUMBER 3
     C                     MOVELD2LNO1    SBLNO1           * LOT NO 1
     C                     MOVELD2LNO2    SBLNO2           * LOT NO 2
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     SBSCHZ           * SCRAP DATE
     C           W@SCFL    IFEQ '1'                        ¬IF_01
     C                     Z-ADDS@YYMD    SBSCHZ           * SCRAP DATE
     C                     END                             ｢IF_01
